ar to $p \\bar{p}$ production. The presence of resonances in the $p \\bar p$\nchannel may destroy the dip at ${\\rm y}_{diff} = 0$. This opens the possibility\nto study diffractively produced resonances. We discuss the observables suited\nfor this purpose.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jan 2018 17:59:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 May 2018 21:08:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-03"}
