ree well with our earlier results for CR protons,\nhelium nuclei, and anti-protons propagation and LIS obtained in the same\nframework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jan 2018 05:30:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-19"}
