s sequential scan procedures to avoid random disk access\nand thus scales to large datasets. We evaluated our work with respect to\naccuracy and performance using several datasets. Experiments show that\n\\emph{ST-Link} is effective in practice for performing spatio-temporal linkage\nand can scale to large datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jan 2018 09:32:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-15"}
