ients are\nsimilar; the cloud rotation periods are much longer than cloud lifetimes and\ncomparable to the galactic rotation period.The rotational kinetic energy is\n1-2\\% of the gravitational potential energy and the cloud edge velocity is well\nbelow the escape velocity, such that cloud-scale rotation probably has little\ninfluence on the evolution of molecular clouds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jan 2018 14:13:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-02"}
